3182a5c283e16a854bb6c849d8669</id><title>10天大美北疆到此一遊</title><updated>2025-07-10T21:01:49+08:00</updated><author><name>諸葛昕妤</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-10T21:01:49+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573181516"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573181516"&gt;Day 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;今次跟返香港嘅旅行團去北疆&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;凌晨1:30機，不過因為天氣唔好，搞到3:00先起飛，未起飛已經坐到腳痺&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🙈&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16362936" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573181516" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250713/20250713_f8188365efaf11895e0ad52uqvQxKMQ8.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d31ec5/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250713/20250713_f8188365efaf11895e0ad52uqvQxKMQ8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16362936_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16362936&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mobile_1.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (1.7 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-13 08:33&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;第一次搭凌晨機，完全瞓唔到，半睡半醒咁捱到去落機&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😵&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;💫&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;飛機8點半左右到，個機場好大好新淨，新疆反恐措施做得好足，檢查行理同入境程序都好嚴謹&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16357799" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="5731815